text: Theodore Gross (February 17, 1880 - December 1, 1951) was an American gymnast. He competed in four events at the 1904 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1880 births Category:1951 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1904 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Louisville, Kentucky
